### Create a new reminder
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "petId": 2,
  "message": "Vet appointment tomorrow",
  "remindAt": "2025-07-30T09:00:00"
}

###

### Get all due reminders (as of now)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reminders/due

###

### Mark a reminder as sent
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/reminders/sent/1

###

### Get all reminders for a specific user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reminders/user/1

###

### Delete a reminder by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/reminders/1

###

### (Optional) Get all reminders for a specific pet
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reminders/pet/1
